ion of everything that makes this truly democratic.</p> \n<p>It is this that Obama, Bush, Cameron, Blair and others are presiding over.</p> \n<p>Little to be proud of and much to be ashamed of.</p>\n                \n            </div>\n            \n                <div class=\"d-comment__actions\">\n                    <div class=\"d-comment__actions__main\">\n                        <a href=\"http://discussion.guardian.co.uk/components/report-abuse/24218928\" class=\"d-comment__action d-comment__action--report\" target=\"_blank\">Report</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            \n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    \n</li>\n\n            \n                \n\n<li class=\"d-comment\n           d-comment--response\n           \n           \"\n    id=\"comment-24219390\">\n    <div class=\"d-comment__inner\">\n        \n        <div class=\"d-comment-header\">\n            <div class=\"d-comment__media\">\n                <span class=\"d-comment__avatar-wrapper\"><img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/discussion/avatars/2013/03/23/11499631/5f80eaec-46a2-499e-85c0-e13dbccafc59/60x60.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"d-comment__avatar\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" /></span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"d-comment__meta\">\n                <div>\n                    <span class=\"d-comment__author\">quak41</span>\n                    \n                    \n                </div>\n\n                <div>\n                    \n                    <time class=\"d-meta-item d-comment__meta-item js-timestamp\"\n                          datetime=\"2013-06-10T17:51:34Z\" data-timestamp=\"1370886694000\">\n                        10 Jun 2013\n                    </time>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"d-comment__main\">\n            <div class=\"d-comment__body\">\n                \n                    <p>@artheart-<br />Thanks for posting a thoughtful response. If I can pick out just one of the things you said<br /></p> \n<blockquote> \n <p><br />to suggest that other people who happen stray from the radical orthodoxy of corporate neoliberalism, and towards criticism - somehow - turns them into &quot;neo-Marxist conspiracy theorists&quot;</p> \n</blockquote> \n<p>Actually I pleased that people dont like orthodox corporate neoliberalism. What Im objecting to is the normalization of blatant untruths, for example the line I quoted from your first post.</p> \n<p>The</p> \n<blockquote> \n <p>US (and the West generally) is effectively a military dictatorship </p> \n <p>No </p> \n</blockquote>it is not. The west is a series of imperfect but liberal democracies, sometimes getting stuff right, sometimes wrong. Pretending that its a dictatorship is insulting to people who suffer actual dictatorship and does nothing to advance any kind of social democracy. \n<p>Try this simple test: stand in the street and shout This country is a military dictatorship. If you are alive the next day, then it isnt.</p>\n                \n            </div>\n            \n                <div class=\"d-comment__actions\">\n                    <div class=\"d-comment__actions__main\">\n                        <a href=\"http://discussion.guardian.co.uk/components/report-abuse/24219390\" class=\"d-comment__action d-comment__action--report\" target=\"_blank\">Report</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            \n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    \n</li>\n\n            \n                \n\n<li class=\"d-comment\n           d-comment--response\n           \n           \"\n    id=\"comment-24219514\">\n    <div class=\"d-comment__inner\">\n        \n        <div class=\"d-comment-header\">\n            <div class=\"d-comment__media\">\n                <span class=\"d-comment__avatar-wrapper\"><img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/discussion/avatars/2010/12/31/brianboru1014/8ddf699a-7787-4b8c-b055-6ef1d5770906/60x60.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"d-comment__avat