1, as yet unused, but for all intents and purposes capable of holding large numbers of people under military guard. </p> \n<p>There has been a coup both in America and indeed here, against the people and democracy of our countries- in the name of free market capitalism, corporate and political centralisation, and authoritarian control over the populations. Grassroots protest movements have no chance in this panopticon, everyone is already so convinced of how free and empowered they are, they don't notice that some chains needn't be shackled to your legs. We're entertained to the point of idiocy, we disconnect from our communities, we consume to feed a false sense of identity empowerment, all the while our countries have become corporate slave states. All our resources, wealth and prosperity is drained upwards into the hands of a few, international business owners and hedge funds, who arm themselves to the teeth against the prospect of popular revolt, monitoring the population to stifle any organic protest movement. </p> \n<p>Oh and I fully expect this comment to end up on a file in my permanent record. Hi.</p>\n                \n            </div>\n            \n                <div class=\"d-comment__actions\">\n                    <div class=\"d-comment__actions__main\">\n                        <a href=\"http://discussion.guardian.co.uk/components/report-abuse/24208196\" class=\"d-comment__action d-comment__action--report\" target=\"_blank\">Report</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            \n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    \n        <ul class=\"d-thread\" data-responses=\"10\">\n            \n                \n\n<li class=\"d-comment\n           d-comment--response\n           \n           \"\n    id=\"comment-24208909\">\n    <div class=\"d-comment__inner\">\n        \n        <div class=\"d-comment-header\">\n            <div class=\"d-comment__media\">\n                <span class=\"d-comment__avatar-wrapper\"><img src=\"http://sta